vosk-dictation (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial release.
  * Core audio capture via rodio with Vosk speech-to-text.
  * Text injection via uinput virtual keyboard.
  * Focus detection for X11 (x11rb) and Wayland (AT-SPI2/zbus).
  * Optional GTK4 floating HUD overlay.

